          "reviewBody": "Attended this wonderful institution for about 8 months back in the early 2000s. Stayed in the hostel, which was an absolute delight. The teachers and staff are very welcoming and make the students feel at home. Infrastructure is top notch and the teaching methods are very intellectually stimulating!\n\nWould recommend the school to any parent looking for the best education for their children.",
