            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "In 1993, I was in class 3rd in this school. Only for 6 months I was in this school’s Hostel . Even today I see pics and all the memories comes in front of my eyes.. Really want to come once and again see my dormitory, assembly ground, n many more. In the evening we used to listen to Raghupati raghav raja ram song in the music room.. can’t remember exactly, I think we all students sang all together",
          "publisher": {
